Package: fsc-btns-source
Architecture: all
Depends: module-assistant, debhelper (>= 5), make, bzip2
Description: Source for the fsc_btns driver.
 This package provides the source code for the fsc_btns kernel modules.
 The fsc-btns package is also required in order to make use of these
 modules. Kernel headers are required to compile these modules.

